data.value: I am Ferit Bulut, a Software Engineering student at Hasan Kalyoncu University. Passionate about coding, I specialize in C#, .NET technologies, and mobile app development with .NET MAUI. I also have experience in Python, C++, and web design. I enjoy solving problems and building innovative software solutions, always aiming to improve my skills and contribute to meaningful projects.
